  "description": "MCP server wrapper for PRSM — Protocol for Research, Storage, and Modeling. Exposes 17 PRSM tools to any MCP-compatible LLM client (Claude Desktop, Cursor, Continue, etc.). Shells out to a local Python install of the prsm-network package; preserves MCP stdio purity.",
  "license": "MIT",
  "homepage": "https://github.com/prsm-network/PRSM",
